 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>LifeCycle </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>定义</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> Spring </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>容器对象的生命周期，任何</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> spring </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>管理对象都可以实现该接口。</span></li>
</ul>

     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> ApplicationContext </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>本身接收启动和停止信号</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> (</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>例如在运行时停止</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> / </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>重启场景</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>) </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>时，</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>Spring </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>容器将在容器上下文中找出所有实现了</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> LifeCycle </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>及其子类接口的类，并调用它们实现的类。它将把这些调用级联到在该上下文中定义的所有</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> Lifecycle </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>实现，然后通过委托</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> LifecycleProcessor </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>来完成此任务</span></li>

style='font-weight:bold'>注</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-size:12.0pt'><span
style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>不能保证会在销毁之前发出停止通知。在常规关闭时，在传播常规销毁回调之前，所有</span><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'> Lifecycle bean </span><span
style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>都首先收到停止通知。但是，在上下文生存期内的热刷新或中止的刷新尝试中，仅调用</span><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'> destroy </span><span style='font-family:
"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>方法</span></p>

<p style='font-size:13.5pt'><span style='font-weight:bold;
font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>自动的生命周期扩展（</span><span style='font-weight:
bold;font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>SmartLifecycle</span><span style='font-weight:
bold;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>）</span></p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>

     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>Lifecycle </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>接口是用于显式启动和停止通知的普通协议，并不意味着在上下文刷新时自动启动。为了对特定</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> bean </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>的自动启动进行精细控制</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> (</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>包括启动阶段</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>)</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>，可以实现</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> SmartLifecycle</span></li>
</ul>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>容器中实现了</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN> Lifecycle
     </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'
     lang=zh-CN>的多个类如果希望有顺序的进行回调时，那么启动和关闭调用的顺序可能很重要。如果任何两个对象之间存在依赖关系，那么依赖方将在依赖后开始，在依赖前停止。然而，有时直接依赖关系是未知的。可能只知道某个类型的对象应该在另一个类型的对象之前开始。在这些情况下，</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>SmartLifecycle
     </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'
     lang=zh-CN>接口定义了另一个选项，即在其继承自</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>Phased</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>的</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN> getPhase</span><span style='font-family:
     "Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US>()</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>方法</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

  <p style='margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:6pt;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
  font-size:11.5pt'><span lang=zh-CN>getPhase</span><span lang=en-US>()</span></p>
  </td>

  <p style='font-family:-apple-system;font-size:11.5pt'><span
  style='background:white'>用于获取组件的执行阶段。</span></p>
  <p style='font-family:-apple-system;font-size:11.5pt'><span
  style='background:white'>方法返回一个整数值，表示组件的执行顺序。具有较小值的组件将先被执行，而具有较大值的组件将后被执行。如果两个组件具有相同的阶段值，则它们将按照它们在应用程序上下文中注册的顺序进行排序</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>当开始时，</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>getPhase</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US>() </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>返回值最小的对象先开始，当停止时，遵循相反的顺序。因此，实现</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>
     SmartLifecycle </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>的对象及其</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN> getPhase() </span><span style='font-family:
     "Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>方法返回</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>
     Integer.MIN_VALUE </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>将在第一个开始和最后一个停止。相反，</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>MAX_VALUE </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>将指示对象应该在最后启动并首先停止</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN> (</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>可能是因为它依赖于要运行的其他进程</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>)</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>。</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>SmartLifecycle
     </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'
     lang=zh-CN>对象的默认</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN> phase </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>是</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN> 0</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>。因此，任何实现类的</span><span style='font-family:
     "Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN> phase </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>的值为负数时都表明一个对象应该在这些标准的生命周期回调之前进行执行，反之亦然</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>SmartLifecycle </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>定义的</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> stop </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>方法接受一个回调。在实现的关闭过程完成之后，任何实现都必须调用回调的</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> run() </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>方法。这允许在必要时进行异步关闭，因为</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> LifecycleProcessor </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>接口，即</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>
     DefaultLifecycleProcessor</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt'>，的默认实现，将等待每个阶段中的对象组的超时值来调用这个回调。默认的每个阶段超时为</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> 30</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>秒。您可以通过在上下文中定义一个名为</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> lifecycleProcessor </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>的</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> bean </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>来覆盖默认的生命周期处理器实例</span></li>
</ul>

 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>LifecycleProcessor </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>接口也定义了用于刷新和关闭上下文的回调方法。后者将简单地驱动关机过程，就好像已经显式地调用了</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> stop() </span><span

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>另一方面，</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>refresh </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>回调支持</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> SmartLifecycle bean </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>的另一个特性。当刷新上下文</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> (</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>在所有对象实例化和初始化之后</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>) </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>时，将调用这个回调，此时，默认的生命周期处理器将检查每个</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> SmartLifecycle </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>对象的</span><span

     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> true</span><span

     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>)</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>。“阶段” 值以及任何 “依赖”
     关系将以如上所述的方式确定启动顺序</span></li>
